    "rowsha": "EMbh09hPBxuGyYEmZW4+osdo1xhZQV+dVMgT1v6N05Y=",
    "originContent": "Let's say you have a list of products, and a user is looking for a \"Czy Swetr,\". Exact match will return nothing, but the fuzzy search will find \"Cozy Sweater.\".",
